reviewText: I am a loyal fan...Love her:)
Westenhoefer is brilliant, both as a comedian and a storyteller. This DVD is one of the best lesbian laughs I've had in forever!

I was at this show in Indianapolis, It was very funny. One of my Straight friends came with me and she laughed as much as I did. I think Suzanne is one of the funniest comics around.
Gay or Straight. If you want a good laugh, Buy this Video.
